DOC.brief_summary: This study evaluate safety efficacy botulinum toxin Type A compare placebo treatment Crow 's Feet Lines ( Lateral Canthal Rhytides ) .
DOC.brief_title: Safety Efficacy Study Botulinum Toxin Type A Treatment Crow 's Feet Lines
DOC.criteria: Moderate severe Crow 's Feet Lines Have adequate vision without use eyeglass assess facial wrinkle mirror ( contact lenses OK ) Current previous botulinum toxin treatment serotype Facial laser light treatment , microdermabrasion superficial peel within 3 month Oral retinoid therapy within 1 year Prior facial cosmetic surgery ( eg , periorbital surgery , facial lift , brow lift , eye lift , eyebrow surgery ) Diagnosis myasthenia gravis , EatonLambert syndrome , amyotrophic lateral sclerosis
